flowchart TD
    A[User Input\nGenres + Artists] --> B[UserProfile Init\nLLM Call]
    B --> C[Numerical Preferences\nenergy, acousticness, valence\ntempo, danceability, loudness\nliveness, speechiness]
    
    C --> D[GMM Inference\npredict_proba]
    E[550k+ Song Catalog\nCSV + Cluster Probabilities] --> D
    D --> F[Cosine Similarity\nUser Vector vs Song Vectors]
    F --> G[Top 100 Candidates]

    G --> H[Weighted Similarity Scoring\n11 features per song]
    C --> H
    H --> I[Ranked Top-K Songs]

    I --> J[Self-Critique LLM\nReliability Score]
    C --> J
    J --> K{Score >= 0.70?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Return Recommendations\n+ Plain English Explanations]
    K -->|No| M[Weight Adjustment LLM\nPersonalized Weights]
    M --> H

    L --> N[User Interaction\nLike / Skip]
    N --> O[EMA Profile Update\nnudge toward liked\npush away from skipped]
    O --> C
